- core:
    - don't let loose tag destroy structure when now parent
      allows it, actions in this case could be:
      - remove/comment loose tag with content
      - find container for a parent
    - merge tags of which only one is allowed (like head for html)
- frontends:
    - commandline:
	--comment-illegal-code
	--discard-comments
	--transform-cdata
    - web xhtmlizer:
	validate, report and deliver bodyshopped version
